                >
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-primary/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-brand-primary text-xl font-bold mr-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
                        >
                            JD
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-lg m-0">
                                James D.
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm m-0">
                                SaaS Founder
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 italic leading-relaxed">
                        "I was skeptical because of the price, but the code
                        quality is top-notch. It saved us months of development
                        time on our internal notification system. It's actually
                        the most fair pricing I've seen in years."
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="bg-brand-bg-card/40 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 p-10 rounded-[2rem] hover:border-brand-primary/30 transition-all duration-500 group"
                >
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-blue/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-brand-blue text-xl font-bold mr-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
                        >
                            SM
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-lg m-0">
                                Sarah M.
